Package org.gbif.occurrencestore.persistence.keygen

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    KeyBuilder
    This interface describes methods that can be used to build unique keys given a string and its "scope".
    KeyPersistenceService<T>
    Implementations of this interface will be responsible for finding, generating and deleting the secondary index keys that are used to lookup entries by their unique identifiers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractHBaseKeyPersistenceService
    An abstract implementation of KeyPersistenceService that handles the finding and deleting of keys in HBase, but leaves the generation of keys to sub-classes.
    HBaseLockingKeyService
    An extension of AbstractHBaseKeyPersistenceService with a generateKey implementation that uses an HBase implementation of the algorithm described at http://dev.gbif.org/code/snippet/CR-OCC-5.
    OccurrenceKeyBuilder
    An implementation of KeyBuilder to provide keys for use as secondary indexes to occurrences in HBase.
    ZkLockingKeyService
    An extension of AbstracHBaseKeyPersistenceService with a generateKey implementation that uses a thread local ZookeeperLockManager to ensure thread-safe key gen.
